00:18:20,320 --> 00:18:25,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那你就不要摆出一副什么都知道的表情…好像什么都看破一般…</font>

269
00:18:26,050 --> 00:18:29,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不要说什么「我还是去死吧」这样的话…</font>

270
00:18:29,840 --> 00:18:33,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你不知道的事情不是还有很多吗？</font>

271
00:18:33,910 --> 00:18:40,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那就像以前一样…对我说「我不是什么都知道  只是知道我知道的事情」啊</font>

272
00:18:43,090 --> 00:18:44,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">而我要死了</font>

273
00:18:44,600 --> 00:18:46,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">被羽川所杀死</font>

274
00:18:46,680 --> 00:18:48,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">为了羽川而死</font>

275
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:52,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">真是的  这是何等的幸福啊</font>

276
00:18:54,230 --> 00:18:59,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我知道自己的行为好像小丑一般  这么做毫无意义</font>

277
00:19:00,100 --> 00:19:03,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">使用怪异杀手的确可以除掉障猫</font>

278
00:19:03,780 --> 00:19:06,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">但羽川所积攒的压力却无从解决</font>

279
00:19:06,950 --> 00:19:08,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">家庭的不和也不会消失</font>

280
00:19:09,620 --> 00:19:14,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">如果这样的结局也可以的话  大概忍野在第一次战斗的时候就已经解决了</font>

281
00:19:15,080 --> 00:19:20,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">刚才忍野欲言又止的那第二个忠告  指的恐怕就是这件事</font>

282
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:23,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">然而  即使这样也好</font>

283
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:27,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我也没想过要帮你  羽川</font>

284
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:32,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">就算是没有意义也好白费也好  我也想为了你而死  仅此而已</font>

285
00:19:46,150 --> 00:19:52,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">因为妖刀把羽川和障猫分离  她们两个之间产生的排斥反应吗？</font>

286
00:19:58,120 --> 00:20:00,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你要干什么啊  猫</font>

287
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:03,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你伤害羽川又有什么用</font>

288
00:20:03,570 --> 00:20:06,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你为了羽川做了那么多</font>

289
00:20:07,410 --> 00:20:12,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不是因为羽川她看到死在路边的你  却丝毫不感到同情吗</font>

290
00:20:13,270 --> 00:20:14,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我也一样</font>

291
00:20:15,350 --> 00:20:16,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（吸血鬼）</font>

292
00:20:15,360 --> 00:20:19,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">被吸血鬼所袭击  无法成为人类的时候</font>

293
00:20:16,690 --> 00:20:18,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（人类）</font>

294
00:20:18,190 --> 00:20:19,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（阿良良木历）</font>

295
00:20:19,910 --> 00:20:22,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">羽川她对我也丝毫没有同情</font>

296
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:22,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（同学）</font>

297
00:20:22,110 --> 00:20:23,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（班长）</font>

298
00:20:22,370 --> 00:20:24,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">从来没有可怜我  从来没有看低过我</font>

299
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:26,070
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（救命恩人）</font>

300
00:20:24,290 --> 00:20:25,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">而是平等地看着我</font>

301
00:20:26,120 --> 00:20:27,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">是这样吧  障猫</font>

302
00:20:28,470 --> 00:20:31,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不管是死在路边也好  被吸血鬼所袭击也好</font>

303
00:20:32,180 --> 00:20:35,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我们一点也不可怜对吧</font>

304
00:20:35,760 --> 00:20:39,700
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你也是喜欢羽川这一点对吧</font>

305
00:20:39,920 --> 00:20:43,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那就不要再这样攻击羽川了</font>

306
00:20:44,230 --> 00:20:47,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">住手！给我住手！求求你给我住手啊！</font>

307
00:20:47,750 --> 00:20:49,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你傻了吧  我的仆从</font>

308
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:57,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">在机器失控的时候胡乱切断电源  当然会伤到机器本身啊</font>

309
00:20:57,150 --> 00:20:57,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（幻听？）</font>

310
00:20:58,900 --> 00:21:02,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">居然拿我的名刀这么乱用</font>

311
00:21:02,500 --> 00:21:06,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你想做怪异的活刺身不成？真让人笑掉大牙</font>

312
00:21:06,030 --> 00:21:06,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（听见了）</font>

313
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:32,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">真是的  还是老样子只会看着眼前啊  我的仆从</font>

314
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:37,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">别以为你可以随便就救活我就可以随便去死</font>

315
00:21:38,050 --> 00:21:41,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你这个白痴  我给你演示一下你就在那里好好看着吧</font>

316
00:21:41,920 --> 00:21:42,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">给我看入迷了吧</font>

317
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:46,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">看好了  怪异杀手是这么用的</font>

318
00:22:13,380 --> 00:22:14,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这样也可以吗</font>

319
00:22:15,780 --> 00:22:17,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这样也可以吧  羽川</font>

320
00:22:18,210 --> 00:22:23,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我们都是这么不值一提  这么不幸  永远无法如愿以偿</font>

321
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:26,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">甚至连挽回都做不到</font>

322
00:22:26,920 --> 00:22:30,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">一辈子都会这样下去  这样也可以吧</font>

323
00:22:32,580 --> 00:22:34,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">怎么可能…可以呢…</font>

324
00:22:57,670 --> 00:23:02,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">第二天  我匆匆吃完早餐  骑上自行车离开了家</font>

325
00:23:03,030 --> 00:23:05,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">去学校之前  我还有一个地方要去</font>

326
00:23:24,770 --> 00:23:25,910
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">那么…</font>

327
00:23:27,300 --> 00:23:28,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这样我就没法摸她的头了</font>

328
00:23:28,870 --> 00:23:29,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊  你说那个啊</font>

329
00:23:30,210 --> 00:23:32,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">吸血鬼小妹要我给她戴的</font>

330
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:40,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">因为这次猫的事件算是全都被她解决了  我就当奖赏的礼物送给她了</font>

331
00:23:40,310 --> 00:23:43,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">该说是希望落空呢  还是说希望本身就是虚幻的呢</font>

332
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:45,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">话说回来  忍野</font>

333
00:23:45,840 --> 00:23:48,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">羽川她没事吧</font>

334
00:23:49,140 --> 00:23:52,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">嗯？啊  没事的  我保证</font>

335
00:23:52,800 --> 00:23:56,790
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">班长小妹对于黄金周的这段事情全都不记得了</font>

336
00:23:57,250 --> 00:23:59,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">身为黑羽川的记忆也…</font>

337
00:24:01,220 --> 00:24:02,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">全都失去了</font>

338
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:05,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">黑羽川？那是啥？</font>

339
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:08,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">指的就是那个状态下的班长小妹啊</font>

340
00:24:08,170 --> 00:24:08,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（不是名字起的好）</font>

341
00:24:08,760 --> 00:24:11,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">用障猫来称呼那个总有些不妥</font>

342
00:24:10,960 --> 00:24:11,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（也不是名字起的坏）</font>

343
00:24:11,380 --> 00:24:11,630
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（只是完美地）</font>

344
00:24:11,730 --> 00:24:14,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">新种必然也要起个新名字</font>

345
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:14,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（用名字诠释了她的身体）</font>

346
00:24:14,340 --> 00:24:16,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">新生的现代妖怪</font>

347
00:24:16,600 --> 00:24:18,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（黑羽川）</font>

348
00:24:16,710 --> 00:24:17,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">黑羽川</font>

349
00:24:18,340 --> 00:24:20,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你命名的眼光也太差了吧</font>

350
00:24:20,470 --> 00:24:21,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（黑色的黝黑的漆黑的腹黑的羽川翼）</font>

351
00:24:21,940 --> 00:24:27,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">对她父母吸收能量的时候  班长小妹的意识其实暂时恢复了一段时间</font>

352
00:24:27,650 --> 00:24:31,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">可以理解为在那一刻她的愿望以某种形式得以实现了吧</font>

353
00:24:31,970 --> 00:24:32,850
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">愿望…</font>

354
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">但是又马上变成了之前的样子</font>

355
00:24:35,360 --> 00:24:41,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不  应该说班长小妹以自己的意愿把已经分离的猫强拉回自己身边</font>

356
00:24:41,520 --> 00:24:43,990
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">并自己附身在猫的身上</font>

357
00:24:44,550 --> 00:24:49,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">在那一瞬间  便宣告了新型怪异————黑羽川的诞生</font>

358
00:24:49,630 --> 00:24:50,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（顺其自然的理想主义）</font>

359
00:24:51,630 --> 00:24:52,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（把一切都归罪于妖怪  推卸责任）</font>

360
00:24:53,630 --> 00:24:54,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="22">{\an8}（我连为羽川而死都没能做到）</font>

361
00:24:55,080 --> 00:24:57,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">忍野  如果说新种的妖怪的话</font>

362
00:24:57,970 --> 00:25:02,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">羽川她岂不是一直被一只叫做「家人」的妖怪所附身的吗</font>

363
00:25:03,190 --> 00:25:08,770
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">家人啊  不过对班长小妹来说父母也不算是家人</font>

364
00:25:08,900 --> 00:25:14,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">正因为如此  对于羽川来说  家人难道就不是怪异一样的存在吗</font>

365
00:25:15,570 --> 00:25:17,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">谁知道呢</font>

366
00:25:21,830 --> 00:25:25,190
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">可是  不管是变成猫还是变成什么</font>

367
00:25:25,350 --> 00:25:29,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">一想到羽川还是羽川这一点  我就忍不住想了很多</font>

368
00:25:30,020 --> 00:25:31,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你们结婚算了</font>

369
00:25:31,910 --> 00:25:32,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">什么？</font>

370
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:36,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我说  阿良良木君你和班长小妹结婚不就可以了吗</font>

371
00:25:36,950 --> 00:25:42,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这样一来班长小妹一直求之而不可得的家族不也就有了吗</font>

372
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:45,670
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这…开玩笑也没有你这么开的啊  忍野</font>

373
00:25:46,130 --> 00:25:49,030
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">是吗  我还觉得这是个不错的办法呢</font>

374
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:53,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">作为春假期间从班长小妹那里获得恩惠的回报</font>

375
00:25:53,320 --> 00:25:55,430
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我觉得这个交易还是蛮不错的</font>

376
00:25:56,930 --> 00:25:59,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这也要看羽川的想法的吧</font>

377
00:25:59,620 --> 00:26:00,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">她当然是有想法的了</font>

378
00:26:02,630 --> 00:26:05,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">正因为有想法才会感到迷惑</font>

379
00:26:05,540 --> 00:26:07,350
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">成为被害者  同时也成为加害者</font>

380
00:26:07,860 --> 00:26:09,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">最终变成怪异</font>

381
00:26:14,960 --> 00:26:18,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">可是  这不是还要看阿良良木君你的想法的吗</font>

382
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:21,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我的…想法？</font>

383
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:27,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我一直还以为你是不是爱上班长小妹了呢</font>

384
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:30,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">你开什么玩笑</font>

385
00:26:32,340 --> 00:26:35,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">我才没爱上羽川</font>

386
00:26:36,180 --> 00:26:36,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">是嘛</font>

387
00:26:38,150 --> 00:26:38,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">是啊</font>

388
00:26:39,800 --> 00:26:41,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">就当作是这样吧</font>

389
00:26:42,200 --> 00:26:44,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">这才是最幸福的选择</font>

390
00:26:45,760 --> 00:26:47,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">如果阿良良木你觉得没问题的话那就这样好了</font>

391
00:26:48,260 --> 00:26:54,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">虽然我姑且问了你一下  可比起你的想法  班长小妹的想法才是最重要的</font>

392
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:58,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">不管障猫做了些什么  不管阿良良木君你做了些什么</font>

393
00:26:58,950 --> 00:27:01,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">人们终究是靠着自己得救的</font>

394
00:27:02,080 --> 00:27:06,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">而且羽川她也从来没想过要求助于谁</font>

395
00:27:06,660 --> 00:27:09,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">如果她来求助于我就好了</font>

396
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:12,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">如果羽川来依靠我  为了她我什么都愿意做</font>

397
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:16,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">说不定她真的寻求过帮助呢</font>

398
00:27:17,520 --> 00:27:18,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">啊？</font>

399
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:23,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="30">又不是只有明明白白地说让你帮忙才算是求助</font>

400
